{
  "stem": "717.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that he worked with my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he didn't know anything about it, whether he came back or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember standing in the street seeing the trucks bringing the people back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I saw a person sitting in the truck with a face smaller than my fist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Until today, I'm not sure whether it was my father or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At the moment, I thought maybe it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this person couldn't live more than another hour something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm still not sure, even now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I remember looking at this person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The truck drove past us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They took them into the Jewish jail in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because later on, I heard different rumors that he was hung there in, in Poznan.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I'm not sure whether I saw him or-- I never told this to my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I'm still not sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We lived with my aunt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember what year this was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Different instructions came in every day, different rules, different laws.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they kept on tearing away people from the families under different pretexts.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "At one time, they needed people that were between 50 and 60, 60 and 70, people with one child, people without children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this particular time, they asked for people that were by themselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my aunt, of course, had no proof that she wasn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she went to the, with the transport.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember my mother helping her pack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember saying goodbye to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never said goodbye to my mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But to her, I said goodbye because she left from our apartment.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
